name: Honda Activa 6G
description: The Honda Activa 6G is a popular scooter known for its reliable performance and comfortable ride. It features a 109.51cc engine, improved suspension, and enhanced fuel efficiency. With a stylish design and convenient features like a spacious under-seat storage and easy handling, the Activa 6G is ideal for daily commuting and city rides.

name: Vespa GTS Super 300
description: The Vespa GTS Super 300 combines high performance with classic Vespa elegance. It features a 278cc engine, advanced ABS braking system, and a comfortable ride. With its sleek design, modern technology, and ample storage, the GTS Super 300 is perfect for both urban commuting and longer journeys.
